snippet.title: Amanda the Adventurer Coming to Console October 10th
snippet.description:
Amanda the Adventurer is coming to Xbox Series X|S, PlayStation 4/5, and Nintendo Switch on October 10th.

For all the news about Amanda, follow the game's socials at: https://x.com/AmandaAdvnturer

For news about DreadXP, follow them at: https://x.com/dreadxpgames
